SYMINGTON _ For much of the past month, Fife Symington has sat in a
U.S. Bankruptcy Court while one of Phoenix's top attorneys has
branded him a liar and a fraud. Day after day, the former Arizona
governor has endured the pounding with remarkable composure and
remained unfailingly upbeat. By JERRY KAMMER. Story will move in
the ``A'' category. &QL; 
