<HEADLINE>
A FIELD TRIP TO THE CAPITAL
 OF GRATITUDE
</HEADLINE>
  (For use by N.Y. Times News Service
 clients) 
 By E.J. MONTINI 
 c.2000 The Arizona Republic 
